# ─── Not published to GitHub — kept locally only ───────────────────────────
# The public repo is trimmed to only what's needed to RUN the sim:
# index.html, sw.js, .nojekyll, js/ (minus js/test/), vendor/, textures/,
# data/, package.json, start.sh, README.md. Everything below stays on this
# machine but is neither tracked nor uploaded.

# Docs — README.md is the one kept exception (repo landing page)
/*.md
!/README.md
/archive/

# Test suite (not needed to run the sim)
/js/test/
/test.sh
/test.html

# Content-generation tooling (regenerates data/*.json)
/scripts/

